The '''Battle Group of [[Yun-Yuuzhan]]''' was one of the five battle groups used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] during the [[Battle of Ebaq]] 9.

==History==
It was under the direct command of [[Warmaster]] [[Tsavong Lah]]. Initially, the Yun-Yuuzhan battle group, along with the [[Yun-Harla]] [[Battle Group of Yun-Harla|battle group]], were kept in reserve. When the Battle turned against Lah, he took a third of the Battle Group of Yun-Yuuzhan with him on the ''[[Jeedai]]'' hunt on [[Ebaq 9]], and ordered the rest to retreat. The Battle Group of Yun-Yuuzhan had the most warning about the minefield that the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] had placed to hamper their retreat, and took the least amount of loses. ''[[Kusurrun]]'' and [[Victory Section]] were part of the group.

